<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Jeevan</title>

    <style>
        body{
            background-color:lightblue;
            font-family:Cambria;
            font-size:14px;
            margin:0;
        }

        .container{
            width:80%;
            margin:auto;
            text-align:center;
            padding:20px;
        }

        h1{
            color:darkblue;
        }

        h2{
            color:blue;
        }

        p{
            color:#003366;
            line-height:1.6;
        }

        marquee{
            color:blue;
            font-weight:bold;
            margin:15px 0;
        }

        .grid{
            display:grid;
            grid-template-columns:repeat(2,180px);
            gap:15px;
            justify-content:center;
            margin:20px;
        }

        .box{
            background:white;
            border:2px solid blue;
            padding:20px;
            border-radius:10px;
            color:blue;
        }

        button{
            background:blue;
            color:white;
            border:none;
            padding:10px 20px;
            font-size:14px;
            cursor:pointer;
            border-radius:5px;
        }

        button:hover{
            background:darkblue;
        }

        .footer{
            margin-top:30px;
            color:navy;
            font-weight:bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

    <h1>Welcome to Jeevan</h1>

    <marquee>
        Welcome to Jeevan - A simple website created using HTML and CSS!
    </marquee>

    <h2>Introduction</h2>

    <p>
        Jeevan is a beginner-friendly website designed to demonstrate the
        basic concepts of HTML and CSS. It showcases text formatting,
        grid layouts, styling, colors, buttons, and scrolling text.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Features</h2>

    <div class="grid">
        <div class="box">HTML Basics</div>
        <div class="box">CSS Styling</div>
        <div class="box">Grid Layout</div>
        <div class="box">Responsive Design</div>
    </div>

    <h2>About Jeevan</h2>

    <p>
        Our goal is to help beginners understand web development in a
        simple and interactive way. HTML provides the structure of the
        webpage, while CSS makes it attractive and visually appealing.
    </p>

    <button>Explore More</button>

    <div class="footer">
        © 2026 Jeevan | Designed using HTML & CSS
    </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
